name: I Want To Break Free - Womxn Develop At Ubisoft 2021
name_original: I Want To Break Free - Womxn Develop At Ubisoft 2021
description:
The game's story is about a princess getting tired of being just the princess character, and deciding she wants to act, and become the main character of her own story.

CONTROLS
Arrows for movement 
Space to jump 
E to interact
Mouse to pick on the menus 

ASSETS
https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/2d/free-2d-mega-pack-177430
along with assets linked in the playlist from TUTO UNITY FR
